  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  dialogueLines:
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: Then listen carefully. The atlas maps debts, favors, and people who pretend
      they only serve drinks.
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: If you return to the barista, stop asking for menus and start asking who
      taught her to keep score.
